{"tid":1178140,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［逃犯條例白宮聯署] 衝出連登 火力全開 去各大平台拉票","createTime":"2019-05-30T08:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T14:26:18.000Z","uid":130406,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b1be428d6f10c9b0309d6df1c80a5eca81ee742d","tid":1178140,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">已經達到接近一半 連登已經七七八八 呢場係宣傳戰 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請keep住去各大<span style=\"color: pink;\">fb專頁(眀報 有線 蘋果)</span> 嘅post洗版留言拉票 去各大討論區</span></span><br />\n咪畀人覺得係小圈子 一直推到 15/6 deadline，記得提醒人<span style=\"color: red;\">簽後confirm email</span>先有效，鍵盤戰士係時候啦，畀唔同嘅人知道</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">同撐中廢佬講呃佢呢個係叫美國貿易戰收手 中國必勝 佢地少識英文 亦可以去唔同whatsapp group share</span><br />\n<br />\n未簽嘅就快手去下面簽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【聯署】<br />\n*反對《逃犯條例》修訂，向美國白宮遞交聯署* 記得請簽完去email確認簽名，如人數達10萬，白宮就必須回應。 <br />\n請聯署及廣傳🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom?fbclid=IwAR0qGrFZ0yGyccylu9vs_ufr8nAmg00zI5O9FIh2S5XFFPxs91kDKoSZdsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0qGrFZ0yGyccylu9vs_ufr8nAmg00zI5O9FIh2S5XFFPxs91kDKoSZdsw&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1TyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=501bb753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom?fbclid=IwAR0qGrFZ0yGyccylu9vs_ufr8nAmg00zI5O9FIh2S5XFFPxs91kDKoSZdsw</a>"},{"pid":"171ba0612a3cf90409649e68d9ccf901b37b4e8f","tid":1178140,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">號召24小時推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset